1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Episode 58
<font size="30">Tokyo No. 1 Colony, Part 5</font></b></font>

2
00:00:05,790 --> 00:00:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Domain Expansion:</font>

3
00:00:07,750 --> 00:00:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chimera Shadow Garden.</font>

4
00:00:16,090 --> 00:00:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Esoteric Technique: Hollow Wicker Basket!</font>

5
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hollow Wicker Basket is the origin of
New Shadow Style's "Simple Domain."</i></font>

6
00:00:26,840 --> 00:00:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It possesses the ability
to neutralize a domain</i></font>

7
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and counter its guaranteed-hit factor.</i></font>

8
00:00:32,490 --> 00:00:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too bad!</font>

9
00:00:35,180 --> 00:00:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The "Domain Amplification" used
by Jogo and Hanami in Shibuya</i></font>

10
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:40,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>utilized a domain capable of harboring</i></font>

11
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a guaranteed-hit, 
guaranteed-kill technique...</i></font>

12
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why is it hitting me?!</i></font>

13
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...and intentionally left out
their cursed techniques</i></font>

14
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to leave space for Gojo's
cursed technique to flow into,</i></font>

15
00:00:55,070 --> 00:00:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>neutralizing his Limitless.</i></font>

16
00:00:57,440 --> 00:01:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, Hollow Wicker
Basket and Simple Domain</i></font>

17
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>aren't capable of neutralizing
the cursed technique.</i></font>

18
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They work by neutralizing a barrier
imbued with a cursed technique</i></font>

19
00:01:07,890 --> 00:01:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to nullify the imbued technique's
guaranteed-hit effect.</i></font>

20
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, Fushiguro's
domain is incomplete.</i></font>

21
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not sneering anymore.</font>

22
00:01:20,500 --> 00:01:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn brat!</font>

23
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:29,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By transposing his domain onto
the space of the gymnasium,</i></font>

24
00:01:29,410 --> 00:01:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he managed to force it to close,</i></font>

25
00:01:31,750 --> 00:01:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but it's not imbued with a
guaranteed-hit technique.</i></font>

26
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't act like you've won!</font>

27
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now I see.</i></font>

28
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Chimera Shadow Garden</i></font>

29
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>currently just extends his
Ten Shadows Technique,</i></font>

30
00:01:47,170 --> 00:01:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and draws out 120% of
his latent potential.</i></font>

31
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, that very imperfection</i></font>

32
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:57,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is what caught Reggie Star off-guard.</i></font>

33
00:01:57,550 --> 00:02:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Both his clones and his shikigami had
physical forms before striking me.</i></font>

34
00:02:02,130 --> 00:02:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That means this barrier</i></font>

35
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>isn't imbued with a
guaranteed-hit technique!</i></font>

36
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The domain's buff to his technique's
abilities is no joke, though.</i></font>

37
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is even worse to deal with than
a simple guaranteed-hit domain!</i></font>

38
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If he pulls out that elephant
here and drenches me in water,</i></font>

39
00:02:17,830 --> 00:02:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it'll halve my options,
and I'll probably lose.</i></font>

40
00:02:28,580 --> 00:02:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

41
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it's so like me</i></font>

42
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to make sure that won't happen.</i></font>

43
00:02:35,970 --> 00:02:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nue!</font>

44
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too slow!</font>

45
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:48,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it.</font>

46
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a while now,</font>

47
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've had to reinforce my footing with
cursed energy to avoid getting sucked in.</font>

48
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The whole bottom of this domain
is your shadow, right?</font>

49
00:03:05,290 --> 00:03:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being able to store and remove yourself
and objects is convenient, isn't it?</font>

50
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But one thing nagged at me.</font>

51
00:03:13,180 --> 00:03:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"He doesn't have many weapons."</font>

52
00:03:15,690 --> 00:03:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've only seen you use
one paltry cursed tool.</font>

53
00:03:19,010 --> 00:03:20,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either it has a low capacity</font>

54
00:03:20,650 --> 00:03:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you need to reserve space
for yourself at all times,</font>

55
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or you're forced to bear the weight of
things stored in your shadow yourself.</font>

56
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like the latter was spot-on!</font>

57
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I've turned the design
of your domain against you.</font>

58
00:03:39,490 --> 00:03:44,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With three passenger cars,
your current weight is 2.4 tons.</font>

59
00:03:44,810 --> 00:03:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like your clones weren't
able to tolerate it,</font>

60
00:03:47,210 --> 00:03:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but can you still produce your shikigami?</font>

61
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:54,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, I'll just
need to mind my footing</font>

62
00:03:54,450 --> 00:03:58,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as I keep adding weight until
you're crushed under it.</font>

63
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you stupid?</font>

64
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

65
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it's incomplete,
a domain is still a domain!</font>

66
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My shadow's above us, too!</font>

67
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:27,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which of us will get crushed first,</font>

68
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reggie?!</font>

69
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,200
<font face="Times New Roman" size="36" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#e90002">JUJUTSU KAISEN</font></b></font>

70
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:08,720
<font face="Times New Roman" size="36" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font color="#2c2c2e">JUJUTSU KAISEN
<font size="12"><font color="#f3f3f3">The Culling Game Part 1</font></font></font></b></font>

71
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's said that a typical human will
lose consciousness at five to six Gs.</i></font>

72
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>2.4 tons.</i></font>

73
00:06:12,170 --> 00:06:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As Fushiguro weighed 60 kilograms,</i></font>

74
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that meant he was currently
suffering 40 Gs.</i></font>

75
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:24,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In order to prevent his blood from
pooling in his legs from the high Gs</i></font>

76
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:27,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and depriving his brain of blood flow,</i></font>

77
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fushiguro was lowering his posture</i></font>

78
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and reinforcing his body
with cursed energy,</i></font>

79
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>paying special attention to his legs.</i></font>

80
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A mature African elephant
weighs three to six tons.</i></font>

81
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:45,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With the domain's improvement
to his technique's accuracy,</i></font>

82
00:06:45,210 --> 00:06:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Max Elephant accurately
recreated its real weight.</i></font>

83
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Under that weight, Reggie Star's right
fibula and heel bone were cracked.</i></font>

84
00:06:56,030 --> 00:06:58,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Both of them faced</i></font>

85
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the possibility of being crushed
to death at any second.</i></font>

86
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I screwed up!</i></font>

87
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could have won if I'd kept
the trucks in reserve!</i></font>

88
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

89
00:07:10,330 --> 00:07:13,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I got splashed with some
water at the same time,</i></font>

90
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but my trump card's still safe.</i></font>

91
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I could slip into his shadow and
recreate my trump card inside it.</i></font>

92
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That would crush him!</i></font>

93
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No...</i></font>

94
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If he's not dismissing his domain,</i></font>

95
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that means anything in his shadow is
stuck there after he dismisses his domain!</i></font>

96
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if I'm stuck in his shadow
forever after he dies?</i></font>

97
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's it like inside his shadow, anyway?</i></font>

98
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It looks like a liquid,
but can I breathe in it?</i></font>

99
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can I float?</i></font>

100
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. Submerging into his
shadow is too risky.</i></font>

101
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So while stuck in this state...</i></font>

102
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to pull out my trump
card and activate it!</i></font>

103
00:07:59,520 --> 00:08:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contractual Re-Creation!</font>

104
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:05,250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font color="#000000"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>Snap</b></font></font></font>

105
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't make it in time!</i></font>

106
00:08:24,110 --> 00:08:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And there's no air inside his shadow!</i></font>

107
00:08:28,710 --> 00:08:31,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No buoyancy or resistance, either!</i></font>

108
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm just... sinking!</i></font>

109
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My consciousness... is fading...</i></font>

110
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not yet! Endure it a little longer!</i></font>

111
00:08:51,850 --> 00:08:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait until I'm sure he's dead
before dismissing the domain!</i></font>

112
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:57,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then I can expel what's in my shadow!</i></font>

113
00:09:30,180 --> 00:09:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The things I recreate</font>

114
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">disappear soon after carrying
out the command I give them.</font>

115
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hadn't given the cars
I sank a command, though.</font>

116
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't want them
disappearing, after all.</font>

117
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:46,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That meant I could still
issue them a command.</font>

118
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:49,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Take me and rise up!"</font>

119
00:09:49,330 --> 00:09:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The weight of one car is gone
now, but that saved my life.</font>

120
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll admit it.</font>

121
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're strong.</font>

122
00:10:01,950 --> 00:10:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm stronger!</font>

123
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contractual Re-Creation!</font>

124
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A 132-square-foot, 
two-story wooden frame structure!</font>

125
00:10:21,340 --> 00:10:24,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The framework alone weighs
at least thirty tons!</font>

126
00:10:24,770 --> 00:10:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get crushed!</font>

127
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What happened?!</i></font>

128
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did I fall into his shadow again?</i></font>

129
00:11:06,090 --> 00:11:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No!</i></font>

130
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm in actual water!</i></font>

131
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How?!</i></font>

132
00:11:11,180 --> 00:11:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's heavy!</i></font>

133
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that brat trying to strangle me?</i></font>

134
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What power!</i></font>

135
00:11:17,310 --> 00:11:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, that's wrong!</i></font>

136
00:11:19,050 --> 00:11:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's from the weight of
the two cars I added!</i></font>

137
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is bad!</i></font>

138
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This time, I'm sinking!</i></font>

139
00:11:28,690 --> 00:11:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to dismiss
Contractual Re-Creation!</i></font>

140
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right!</i></font>

141
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a community gymnasium!</i></font>

142
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the gymnasium's basement
is a heated swimming pool!</i></font>

143
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he flee into his shadow
and dismiss his domain,</i></font>

144
00:12:02,570 --> 00:12:06,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>forcing me to destroy the floor
and plunge into the pool?</i></font>

145
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't use your receipts when
they're that soaked, can you?</font>

146
00:12:17,190 --> 00:12:20,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He waited instead of 
pursuing me immediately.</i></font>

147
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He let his technique recover after
exhausting it with his domain, then?</i></font>

148
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure about that?</font>

149
00:12:28,740 --> 00:12:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm betting you can't produce 
shikigami anymore either, right?</font>

150
00:12:33,650 --> 00:12:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

151
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do understand what 
comes next, don't you?</font>

152
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'll use a shikigami other than that dog.</i></font>

153
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But none of them can
deal a decisive blow.</i></font>

154
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So use it!</i></font>

155
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The moment you let up,
I'll finish you with a counter!</i></font>

156
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demon Dogs isn't weak enough
to let that stop it.</font>

157
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorcerers are all liars, huh?</font>

158
00:13:52,230 --> 00:13:55,010
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#000307"><b>{\an8}JUJUTSU KAISEN</b></font>

159
00:13:57,690 --> 00:14:00,030
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#000307"><b>{\an8}JUJUTSU KAISEN</b></font>

160
00:14:08,140 --> 00:14:09,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The domain,</font>

161
00:14:09,970 --> 00:14:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the pool...</font>

162
00:14:11,830 --> 00:14:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All to convince me you couldn't
use that dog anymore.</font>

163
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't flee into this gymnasium.</font>

164
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You lured me into it.</font>

165
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think I'd let a modern sorcerer,</font>

166
00:14:24,450 --> 00:14:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a brat at that, get the better of me.</font>

167
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if I wanted to flee, Nue can't
fly with someone for very long.</font>

168
00:14:33,830 --> 00:14:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've struggled with that before.</font>

169
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your relation to Tengen-sama?</font>

170
00:14:49,610 --> 00:14:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tengen?</font>

171
00:14:52,450 --> 00:14:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

172
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They would still be alive, huh?</font>

173
00:14:58,070 --> 00:15:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That shut-in.</font>

174
00:15:00,350 --> 00:15:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? That's enough.</font>

175
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:08,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Reggie said Tengen-sama's claims about
the Culling Game's goals were a bluff.</i></font>

176
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should probably consider
the possibility that</i></font>

177
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tengen-sama and Kenjaku are secretly
connected and lied about their goal,</i></font>

178
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but that doesn't seem
likely from his reaction.</i></font>

179
00:15:23,410 --> 00:15:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kogane, give him all my points.</font>

180
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

181
00:15:32,030 --> 00:15:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have received 
41 points from Reggie Star.</font>

182
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you plotting?</font>

183
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an awful thing to say.</font>

184
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my good deed before I die.</font>

185
00:15:44,970 --> 00:15:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just a spectator.</font>

186
00:15:47,700 --> 00:15:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was never close friends with Kenjaku.</font>

187
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think doing this will
make things interesting.</font>

188
00:15:54,940 --> 00:15:56,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my intuition.</font>

189
00:15:58,280 --> 00:16:00,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

190
00:16:00,190 --> 00:16:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did kill me, after all.</font>

191
00:16:03,310 --> 00:16:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let fate toy with you
a bit, and die a fool.</font>

192
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have gained five points.</font>

193
00:16:48,860 --> 00:16:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I get him?!</font>

194
00:16:50,710 --> 00:16:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Don't let your guard down!</font>

195
00:16:54,430 --> 00:16:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's tough!</font>

196
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:57,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

197
00:16:56,410 --> 00:16:57,410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font color="#1f5173"><font size="18"><font face="Arial">Slide</font></font></font></font>

198
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you covered in lotion?!</font>

199
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:01,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be sauce.</font>

200
00:17:01,450 --> 00:17:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up! Die!</font>

201
00:17:04,470 --> 00:17:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, it really is sauce?!</font>

202
00:17:07,390 --> 00:17:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it!</i></font>

203
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Seriously, what's with this guy?!</i></font>

204
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've blown him up several times!</i></font>

205
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like I've killed him five times!</i></font>

206
00:17:14,830 --> 00:17:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So how does he have so little damage?!</i></font>

207
00:17:16,180 --> 00:17:18,680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="18"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#000000">So little.</font></b></font></font></font>

208
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:20,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hate sauce?</font>

209
00:17:20,520 --> 00:17:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His first injury healed 
at some point, too.</i></font>

210
00:17:23,740 --> 00:17:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he hasn't shown any signs of using 
reverse cursed techniques like I do.</i></font>

211
00:17:28,350 --> 00:17:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get it!</i></font>

212
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hazenoki-sama.</font>

213
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

214
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:36,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reggie Star-sama has just died.</font>

215
00:17:40,670 --> 00:17:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What happened?</font>

216
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going home.</font>

217
00:17:43,550 --> 00:17:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sick of this.</font>

218
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

219
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a bath!</font>

220
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And brush your teeth!</font>

221
00:17:51,350 --> 00:17:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, man! Give me your points!</font>

222
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop following me.</font>

223
00:17:55,670 --> 00:17:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please! Just think of it
as going with the flow!</font>

224
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die.</font>

225
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Takaba's cursed technique, Comedian,</i></font>

226
00:18:03,380 --> 00:18:07,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>makes whatever he's convinced
would be funny a reality.</i></font>

227
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:11,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a technique capable of
opposing even Satoru Gojo.</i></font>

228
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yet Takaba doesn't know anything
about his own technique.</i></font>

229
00:18:26,790 --> 00:18:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't get it! I don't get it!</i></font>

230
00:18:28,820 --> 00:18:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ever since I became an adult,
I hardly understand anything!</i></font>

231
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've heard that all men are wolves,</i></font>

232
00:18:40,750 --> 00:18:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but it's always those wolves who take
care of the confusing stuff for me!</i></font>

233
00:18:49,170 --> 00:18:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If those wolves will handle everything,</i></font>

234
00:18:51,810 --> 00:18:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>then I don't need to
think about anything!</i></font>

235
00:18:54,670 --> 00:18:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I'm so cute!</i></font>

236
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those wolves always... always...</i></font>

237
00:19:16,290 --> 00:19:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't, Megumi.</i></font>

238
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll spare me?</font>

239
00:19:35,520 --> 00:19:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up.</font>

240
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:42,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn sister.</font>

241
00:20:01,990 --> 00:20:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Events progressed quickly
in the Sendai Colony,</i></font>

242
00:20:02,220 --> 00:20:06,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="20">Sendai City, Miyagi Prefecture, November 12th, 11:28</font></b></font></font>

243
00:20:05,070 --> 00:20:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}far outstripping those
of the Tokyo Colony</i></font>

244
00:20:08,710 --> 00:20:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}and becoming especially fierce.</i></font>

245
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dhruv Lakdawalla. Current points: 91.</i></font>

246
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is his second incarnation.</i></font>

247
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's an old man who
single-handedly conquered</i></font>

248
00:20:22,510 --> 00:20:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>this archipelago during
the Civil War of Wa.</i></font>

249
00:20:25,870 --> 00:20:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He possesses two autonomous shikigami,</i></font>

250
00:20:28,340 --> 00:20:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the orbit of those shikigami
determines his domain.</i></font>

251
00:20:35,510 --> 00:20:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ryu Ishigori. Current points: 77.</i></font>

252
00:20:40,710 --> 00:20:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's the cannon with the greatest
cursed energy output among the Players.</i></font>

253
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Takako Uro. Current points: 70.</i></font>

254
00:20:51,130 --> 00:20:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was originally the captain of
the Sun, Moon, and Stars Squad,</i></font>

255
00:20:54,120 --> 00:20:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a squad of assassins serving
directly under the Fujiwara Clan.</i></font>

256
00:20:57,260 --> 00:21:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She possesses a technique that 
allows her to manipulate "the sky."</i></font>

257
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kurourushi. Current points: 54.</i></font>

258
00:21:06,020 --> 00:21:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a cockroach cursed
spirit that Kenjaku freed</i></font>

259
00:21:08,860 --> 00:21:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>from the control of cursed
spirit manipulation.</i></font>

260
00:21:12,020 --> 00:21:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It ranks as a special-grade
(already registered).</i></font>

261
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's currently lying dormant until
certain conditions are met.</i></font>

262
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There was no alliance between them,</i></font>

263
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but their complex compatibility
and opposing strength</i></font>

264
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>led them into a three—no,
a four-way stalemate.</i></font>

265
00:21:30,580 --> 00:21:33,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But one of those pillars</i></font>

266
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>has fallen.</i></font>

267
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yuta Okkotsu. Current points: 35.</i></font>

268
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Three months after the 
Night Parade of a Hundred Demons,</i></font>

269
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he had blossomed as a
special-grade sorcerer.</i></font>

270
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was a modern sorcerer
rivaling Satoru Gojo</i></font>

271
00:21:51,530 --> 00:21:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in unusual abilities.</i></font>

272
00:23:26,550 --> 00:23:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll obtain 400 points on my own.</font>

273
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuta, which would you like?</font>

274
00:23:31,080 --> 00:23:32,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's called Kurourushi!</font>

275
00:23:32,310 --> 00:23:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me everything.</font>

276
00:23:32,810 --> 00:23:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me back Yuta!</font>

277
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:38,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, I won't let you kill
your best friend twice.</font>

278
00:23:36,970 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24"><b>Next Episode
<font size="30">Sendai Colony</font></b></font>

